OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOne of the terms of a plan to
OL,8,Frestructure Thames Water "holds the
OL,9,Fcompany to ransom", the High Court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe utility, which is England's
OL,13,Fbiggest water company with about 16
OL,14,Fmillion customers in London and the
OL,15,FThames Valley, is in about #16 billion
OL,16,Fof debt and needs #3.3 billion over
OL,17,Fthe next five years to keep running,
OL,18,Fwith money due to run out by late
OL,19,FMarch.
