OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAt a hearing last month, a High Court
OL,8,Fjudge allowed a restructuring plan
OL,9,Fknown as the "A plan" to be put to
OL,10,Fcreditors for approval, which would
OL,11,Fprovide a loan of up to #3 billion
OL,12,Fwith a 9.75% interest rate.
OL,14,FBut a group of secondary creditors has
OL,15,Fproposed an alternative known as the
OL,16,F"B plan" which they claim would
OL,17,Fprovide the company with the same
OL,18,Ffunding on better terms.
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@UO]xD@AOUxD@HO]
