OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOn Monday, barristers for Class B
OL,8,Fcreditors told a hearing in London
OL,9,Fthat a term of the "A plan" known as
OL,10,Fthe "June release condition" (JRC)
OL,11,Fwould allow Class A creditors to
OL,12,F"dictate" the terms of further funding
OL,13,Fbeyond June 30 if certain conditions
OL,14,Fare not met.
OL,16,FTony Singla KC, for the Class B
OL,17,Fcreditors, told the court the JRC
OL,18,Fwould allow Class A creditors to
OL,19,F"wrestle control of this company and
OL,20,Fcall the shots".
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@[O]rD@EOUrD@\O]tD@AOUtD@IO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU|D@OO]
