OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said: "The JRC holds the company to
OL,8,Fransom because unless these conditions
OL,9,Fare met the company will risk entering
OL,10,Finto (special administration).
OL,12,F"It is putting the company into the
OL,13,Fposition whereby the Class A will be
OL,14,Fable to say 'We are not releasing any
OL,15,Ffurther funding'.
OL,17,F"The JRC gives the Class A creditors a
OL,18,Fright to veto. It allows them to
OL,19,Fdirect the way in which this future
OL,20,Frecapitalisation process will go."
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@bO]
