OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Singla said the Class B creditors
OL,8,Fwished to compile a "24-page expert
OL,9,Freport" on the impact of the JRC as
OL,10,Fpart of a "very targeted and focused
OL,11,Fattack", adding if their case were
OL,12,Fcorrect, it would be "the end" of the
OL,13,F"A plan".
OL,15,FTom Smith KC, for Thames Water
OL,16,FUtilities Holdings Ltd (TWUH), one of
OL,17,Fthe companies which form Thames Water
OL,18,FGroup (TWG), said the bid by Class B
OL,19,Fcreditors was an "omnishambles".
