OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Justice Trower dismissed the bid to
OL,8,Fcompile the report, ruling the Class B
OL,9,Fcreditors "have not established that
OL,10,Fthis evidence is reasonably required".
OL,12,FThe hearing comes amid the company's
OL,13,Fefforts to shore up its finances with
OL,14,Fa bailout from investors.
OL,16,FIt owns more than 20,000 miles of
OL,17,Fwater mains and more than 68,000 miles
OL,18,Fof sewers across London, the Thames
OL,19,FValley and the Home Counties, with
OL,20,Fapproximately 8,000 employees.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@eO]
