OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIt has been at the centre of growing
OL,8,Fpublic outrage over the extent of
OL,9,Fpollution, rising bills, high
OL,10,Fdividends and executive pay and
OL,11,Fbonuses at the UK's privatised water
OL,12,Ffirms.
OL,14,FMr Smith told a hearing in December
OL,15,Fthat the company's funds would be
OL,16,F"exhausted" by March 24 2025 if the
OL,17,Frestructuring was not approved and
OL,18,Fthat there was a "public interest in
OL,19,Fhaving Thames Water on a stable
OL,20,Fplatform".
