OL,7,FTwo days after that hearing, regulator
OL,8,FOfwat announced the company would be
OL,9,Fallowed to hike consumer bills by 35%,
OL,10,Fdespite its asking to raise prices by
OL,11,F59%, and would also be fined #18.2
OL,12,Fmillion for paying "unjustified"
OL,13,Fdividends to shareholders.
