OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe "A plan", drawn up by a cluster of
OL,8,Finvestment giants including BlackRock,
OL,9,FAbrdn and M&G, would effectively
OL,10,Fguarantee Thames Water can keep
OL,11,Foperating until 2026 by providing #1.5
OL,12,Fbillion of funding, with a further
OL,13,F#1.5 billion potentially available and
OL,14,Fpayment dates for its debts extended
OL,15,Fby two years before a larger
OL,16,Frestructuring due later this year.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@LO]
