OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe court was told it had been
OL,8,Fapproved by creditors holding more
OL,9,Fthan 75% of its Class A debt, which is
OL,10,Fworth about #11.5 billion and is the
OL,11,Fleast risky class of bonds in its debt
OL,12,Fpile.
OL,14,FThis is opposed by a secondary group
OL,15,Fof creditors who hold a smaller
OL,16,Fportion of Thames Water's debt worth
OL,17,Fabout #750 million, made up of riskier
OL,18,FClass B bonds.
