OL,3,CPart of Thames Water restructure plan
OL,4,C'holds company to ransom', High Court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FTheir lawyers have told the court that
OL,8,Ftheir alternative "B plan" also
OL,9,Finvolves a #3 billion loan but with
OL,10,Fdifferent terms, including an 8%
OL,11,Finterest rate and no JRC, and was
OL,12,F"clearly more attractive".
OL,14,FMr Justice Trower ruled the "A plan"
OL,15,Fcould be put to creditors at seven
OL,16,Fmeetings last month, which if approved
OL,17,Fcould be rubber-stamped at a final
OL,18,Fhearing, known as a sanctioning
OL,19,Fhearing, due to be held across four
OL,20,Fdays in early February.
